Title: Invisibobble Traceless Ring True Black Rubber Band(Black)
Description: Time to say goodbye to marks and split ends! This knight in spiral armor puts an end to all problems you’ve had tying up your hair! Where does the name invisibobble come from? invisibobble was created by the blending of the words ‚invisible’ and ‚bobble’. Thus, the construction of ‚invisibobble’ reflects the characteristic feature of the invisibobble: it leaves no trace in the hair after being worn. What’s special about the invisibobble? The invisibobbles has many advantages over a regular hairtie: doesn’t leave a kink in your hair, revolutionary styling tool, non-soaking, avoids split ends and hair breakage, avoids headaches, no tugging or pulled hairs, strong hold, antiallergic, compatible with all hair types. Is the invisibobble also suited for allergy sufferer and neurodermatitis? Due to the smooth surface of the invisibobble, bacteria cannot collect within the hair bobble. Additionally, the invisibobble is very easily cleaned. The invisibobble is therefore more hygienic than other hairties, and is hence particularly suited for allergy sufferer or neurodermatitis.
CategoryName: Health and Beauty>Hair Care>Hair Care Accessories>Hair Accessories

Title: Lotus Radiant Gold Cellular Glow Facial Kit ( 37g * 4 = 148g) 148 g(Set of 4)
Description: Product Description:Radiant Gold -Cellular Glow Facial kit is the perfect way to achieve a flawless golden Glow. All it takes is 4 easy steps and the Glow you have always wanted is yours, in just 30 minutes.How to use : 1st step – Clean your face by Using Cleanser. 2nd step – Apply Activator 3rd step – Massage with Masaage cr�me 4th step – Apply Mask and wipe off with either damp cotton or wash off with water.Packaging: This gold kit comes in a beautiful gold cardboard box with all the details of this product. In that shiny box, there are 4 pouches of cleansing scrub, activator, massage cream & mask. This is a 4-step facial procedure. I like this mini, travel sized packaging, but it can be used twice. So for that second use, it does not look super hygienic. It is easy and is reasonably priced.1. Cleansing ScrubThis cleansing scrub is the first step of this facial. The light yellow scrub has a medium thick consistency with some yellow gold particles. It is creamy, but not super gentle on skin. You need to be careful during application. I gently apply this on face and massage it in circular motion for 5 minutes, and then rinse with water. It smoothly cleanses all the dirt and oil from my face and gives a very clear glow.2. Gold ActivatorRadiant gold activator has a unique gel based formula with some micro shimmery gold particles. I require 5-6 drops for my skin and then I massage it all over my face for 3 minutes. It feels light and smooth on skin. It gives a nice glow and hydrates the skin. I totally love this step. It acts as a skin highlighter actually and makes skin radiant and glowing. This step doesn’t need any clean up.3. Massage CreamThis is the most important step of the facial. Massage can make your skin glow, if done in the right way. This massage cream comes with a soft, creamy consistency which glides easily on skin and makes skin extremely soft. It takes around 10-15 minutes to complete this procedure. After that, I cleanse my face with a sponge. This massage cream provides a healthy glow without making my skin oily. As it is a thick cream, it dries out during massage and you require more product. It smells nice and has never irritated my skin.4. MaskRadiant gold mask is the 4th and the last step in this facial. The mask has a yellow colored, thick, creamy consistency. It spreads nicely on my face. But again it is quite thick, so decent amount of product is needed to cover up my entire face. It takes few minutes to get dry and then you can remove it with a sponge. It feels a little dry, maybe for the weather, but it definitely makes my skin glow.Overall: I like this facial kit. It is really a nice product for instant use. I do not like to go to parlors for facials; I always believe in natural ingredients. But I have used this before a party, where I needed instant glow as I was sick, and it worked really great. I am not sure about the potency of gold particles used in this product but this facial feel nice on skin.My sick and dull face looked brighter and glowing after using this kit. It looked healthy and felt soft as well as moisturized. But the only con is that the glow doesn’t stay for long. After 3 days, again, I had a party but my face didn’t look as glowy. It is just an instant glow kit. As this brand uses natural ingredients, this facial suits my skin well and has never broken me out. Also, it keeps my skin oil- free.Pros of Lotus Herbals Radiant Gold Cellular Glow Facial Kit:• Compact packaging & affordable• Travel friendly• All the products are nice and smooth in texture• Nice fragrance• Gives a nice, instant glow to dull face• Makes skin healthy• Helps to remove skin darkness a bit• Gives soft and hydrated skin• Keeps skin oil-free• Never broke me outCons of Lotus Herbals Radiant Gold Cellular Glow Facial Kit:• Effect doesn’t stay for long• Scrub is not gentle enough for sensitive skin
